Read How to sew an ipod case for more ideas. Make the Christmas tree skirt from felt. Felt is ideal for covering the base of the Christmas tree. Red felt is a good color for this purpose. Make cards from felt. Use scrap pieces of felt to create Christmas designs on card that provide a lovely raised, tactile feel to the card. Read the homemade cards articles on wikiHow for more ideas.
